title: #173 - Gus & Eddy
description:
On this episode of the H3 Podcast we are joined by comedians, YouTubers, and all around good boys- Gus Johnson & Eddy Burback of the Gus & Eddy Podcast! Together we discuss Eddy's sporadic upload schedule, how they split up household chores, Gus putting together a go bag, Jaystation being arrested, Corona virus, commercials that make you cry, Norm McDonald being the GOAT, butt hole candles, and a whole lot more!
